        <span></span><span></span><span></span>
        <b>agent_manifest.json</b>
      </div>
      <pre><code><span class="prompt">$ </span><span class="cmd">ethbeijing init --year 2026</span>
<span class="out">→ Resolving manifest...</span>
<span class="out">→ Fetching </span><span class="key">/tracks</span>
<span class="ok">✓ ai_x_web3</span><span class="out"> ............ active</span>
<span class="out">→ Loading prize_pool ... </span><span class="ok">$5,000 USD</span>

<span class="prompt">$ </span><span class="cmd">agent.spawn --role hacker</span>
<span class="out">→ Booting model: </span><span class="str">"gpt-on-chain"</span>
<span class="out">→ Memory: </span><span class="key">ipfs://0xbeijing</span>
<span class="out">→ Wallet: </span><span class="key">0x...c0de</span>
<span class="ok">✓ READY.</span>
<span class="prompt">$ </span><span class="cmd">build --idea </span><span class="str">"&lt;your_idea&gt;"</span>

<span class="cursor"></span></code></pre>
